REST API for mobile using best practices

Documentation
-------------

The full documentation is at https://django_mobile_rest_api.readthedocs.io.

Quickstart
----------

Install Django Mobile REST API::

    pip install django_mobile_rest_api

Add it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:

.. code-block:: python

    INSTALLED_APPS = (
        ...
        'django_mobile_rest_api.apps.DjangoMobileRestApiConfig',
        ...
    )

Add Django Mobile REST API's URL patterns:

.. code-block:: python

    from django_mobile_rest_api import urls as django_mobile_rest_api_urls


    urlpatterns = [
        ...
        url(r'^', include(django_mobile_rest_api_urls)),
        ...
    ]
